{"tid":1332961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友做看更同住公屋，猶豫嫁唔嫁俾佢","createTime":"2019-07-19T13:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:10:23.000Z","uid":21488,"like":6,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3406c131723be3604d08f3ebafb9221870488032","tid":1332961,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友都已經三字頭，一開始識佢果陣已經知佢住公屋同做屋苑看更，但一齊果陣佢話會俾心機轉行同買私樓，我選擇信左佢。然後而家隔左三年，佢都仲係做緊同一間既看更；仲係唔會儲夠錢買私樓。質問佢佢話「依家咁樣都幾好吖」，真係俾佢激死！我唔係話拜金，但見佢咁唔上進，我真係冇信心將自己未來交俾佢。佢一直都話拍拖第四或第五年結婚，我真心想卻步！"},{"pid":"6e21f4c61bb884d3c1ed44b62602d9a6d01daae6","tid":1332961,"uid":21488,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"穩定居所 穩定職業 樓主嫁比佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1949beeee79fc87acc8eb74b7c0c1789e6ce855","tid":1332961,"uid":70205,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"唉，想同鄭若驊性交"},{"pid":"47b555d48522e86fa21a6865d8732d92cdb0375f","tid":1332961,"uid":29070,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"終於叫左雞破處。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251433</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9aa5e770cefd5eba5e886119c55b8780a6d2d6a1","tid":1332961,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"咁你又咩職業住咩樓? 點解唔可以你買私樓?"},{"pid":"18f9d4a51355855ea8cfea532cd5bfc53c3a33da","tid":1332961,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"走囉<br />\n反正有張八達通係身<br />\n點都會搵到地方比人嘟既"},{"pid":"cfc0d68ad17f131c58d3e3cbbb9bc7702191f097","tid":1332961,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"47b555d48522e86fa21a6865d8732d92cdb0375f","tid":1332961,"uid":29070,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"終於叫左雞破處。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251433